'''Ruth Mompati''' (14 Loetse 1925 - 12 Mots'eanong 2015) e ne e le ralipolotiki oa [[Aforika Borwa]] ebile e le e mong oa baetapele ba Basali ba Mmesa ka la 9 Phato 1956.<ref>http://www.sahistory.org.za/people/ruth-mompati</ref>

== Tsa bonyaneng le thuto ==
Ruth Mompati o tshotshwe ko bontlheng jwa le fatshe jwa Bokone Bophirima. Ka morago gwa go fetsa dithuto tsa gagwe tsa mophato wa borataro, a berekela lelwapa la batho ba basweu morago ga nako a tsena Tygerkloof Terachers Training College.

== Tsa Tiro ==
Go tswa 1953 go fitlha 1961 odirile mmereko jwa motlanyi adirela Nelson Mandela le Oliver Tambo ko di ofising tsa bona tsa molao. A nna leloko la mokgatlho jwa African National Congress ka 1954 a be a kgethiwa gonna leloko la komiti jwa baakamedi ba mokgatlho jwa basadi mo setshabeng jwa African National Congress. A tlhopiwa go nna leloko la palamente ka ditlhopo tsa ntlha tsa temokrasi tsa Aforika Borwa ka ngwaga wa 1994, a tlhomiwa moemedi wa Aforika Borwa ko Switzerland go tloga ka 1996 fo fitlha 2000, a nna matoropo wa Vryburg morago gwa go boa ko Switzerland, mme a bereka e le mookame jwa leloko jwa Ukhondo we Sizwe Veteran's Association.  

== Tsa Loso ==
O thokafetse ka 12 Motsheganong 2015 ka mogago gwa bolwetse bo bokhutswane ko bokelong jwa Kapa Bophirima.

